        <div class="bug-title">#3 - Navbar Page Title Visibility Issue</div>
        <div class="bug-description">When users click on the navbar links containing texts such as About, Features, Partners, etc., the title of the respective page is slightly cut or not visible.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="upcoming-features" style="margin-top: 40px; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
