            <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right" style="color: #007bff; margin-right: 5px;"></i>Link Tags: Organize your links effortlessly by assigning tags for better categorization.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right" style="color: #007bff; margin-right: 5px;"></i>Password Protection: Safeguard your shortened links by adding an extra layer of security with password protection.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

</div>
</body><%- include('partials/footer') %>
